{"tid":14574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴治奧串爆蘇永康：我無吸毒","createTime":"2016-11-30T14:28:00.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T22:31:43.000Z","uid":5195,"like":212,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81cbf0c0ee76bdd4db82a63816b45a7d87e9236d","tid":14574,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:28:00.000Z","msg":"歌手蘇永康的圈外太太已懷孕五個月，他今日接受傳媒訪問時，表示不希望兒子成為「梁天恆、游蕙禎」等「造反嘅人」，若兒子日後分裂國家會「親手懲戒」。梁頌恆晚上在facebook貼上一碗湯的照片，並以蘇永康的歌詞回應：「我放任自負 懶理會某君不喜歡」。<br />\n<br />\n梁頌恆撰文回應蘇永康，形容回家後即獲母親端上靚湯，又指從政令母親被跟蹤被騷擾，「雖然我無吸毒，但令媽咪終日憂心忡忡」，實在心中有愧，又指家人一直支持他，母親又陪他擺街站，「我知道，她心裡的我，比甚麼都寶貴。」"},{"pid":"c9cbb0b594c687625dc791d7dc5559c6b2bf3ad5","tid":14574,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:30:14.000Z","msg":"巴神好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f9e576869c00df68d22f22ef78f8ffd3e99288","tid":14574,"uid":8577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:33:20.000Z","msg":"嗱，巴治奧呢獲我就撐你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d7b446ac571aca07bbc78c0540dc547254e1fb","tid":14574,"uid":22080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:33:29.000Z","msg":"抽得靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"177cba5fa2f96f59ac6bb7313fb27faeec146d71","tid":14574,"uid":34949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:34:54.000Z","msg":"抽到乾晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d876bd5f53e82ab46b962efa39e7d717e10c1b2","tid":14574,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:37:03.000Z","msg":"呢次又抽得好靚, 讚下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6667641484b25b44a902cd95da6db41d03736e64","tid":14574,"uid":18281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:38:57.000Z","msg":"Ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" cl